{
  "stem": "1753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 80.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We-- over the year and one week that I was in Treblinka, not to mention the previous four-- four years, but in particular in Treblinka, have seen hundreds, and hundreds, and hundreds of people being shot to death, beaten to death, tortured to death, hung, beaten to death with a trunk of wood, for a variety of reasons, or no reasons.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we knew our days would be numbered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] On July [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] 14, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just exactly one week before they eliminated the camp-- was the 14th or the 16th-- 5 days before, it must have been-- would have been the 16th. 16th, that's correct.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Five days-- 16th and 17th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I have it recorded. 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were preparing to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we prepared ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had all our orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was only one barrack that was divided in the group that had families, and wives, husbands, respectively.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some of them were true marriages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some of them were arranged marriages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the other side for the men, most of them were men, which was the-- the workers' barrack, we knew what we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were going to, about 5 o'clock the next morning, to escape the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And all 550 would run towards the fences.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There are three types, the inner fence, the middle fence, and then the-- the-- the-- the [INAUDIBLE] nets, which is the-- the kind of wire where you can easily get caught in it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That we would take our blankets, we would storm the fences, we would do away with the guards.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
